replies.body:
I've been asked both if he'll be nerfed and if he'll be buffed D:

{{sticker:sg-janna}} 


...real answer, champions that work differently with critical strike (Yasuo, Tryndamere, Gangplank, Ashe, Jhin, even stuff like Corki) will need to be watched but it's not at all clear which of them are nerfed and buffed yet, so follow-up is more likely than pre-release changes, unless there's a design quality issue to be handled.
